### Banking Transactions API - Sample Requests
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### =====================
### CREATE TRANSACTIONS
### =====================

### Create a transfer between accounts
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "toAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "amount": 250.00,
  "currency": "USD",
  "type": "transfer"
}

### Create a deposit
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-00000",
  "toAccount": "ACC-12345",
  "amount": 1000.50,
  "currency": "EUR",
  "type": "deposit"
}

### Create a withdrawal
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "ACC-67890",
  "toAccount": "ACC-00000",
  "amount": 75.25,
  "currency": "GBP",
  "type": "withdrawal"
}

### =====================
### LIST TRANSACTIONS
### =====================

### Get all transactions
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions

### Filter by account ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345

### Filter by type
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions?type=transfer

### Filter by date range
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions?from=2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z&to=2024-12-31T23:59:59.999Z

### Combined filters (account + type)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions?accountId=ACC-12345&type=deposit

### =====================
### GET TRANSACTION BY ID
### =====================

### Get a specific transaction (replace with actual ID from create response)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions/replace-with-actual-uuid

### =====================
### ACCOUNT BALANCE
### =====================

### Get account balance
GET http://localhost:3000/api/accounts/ACC-12345/balance

### =====================
### ACCOUNT SUMMARY
### =====================

### Get account summary
GET http://localhost:3000/api/accounts/ACC-12345/summary

### =====================
### INTEREST CALCULATION
### =====================

### Calculate simple interest (5% rate, 30 days)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/accounts/ACC-12345/interest?rate=0.05&days=30

### =====================
### CSV EXPORT
### =====================

### Export all transactions as CSV
GET http://localhost:3000/api/transactions/export?format=csv

### =====================
### VALIDATION ERROR EXAMPLE
### =====================

### Invalid request - demonstrates validation errors
POST http://localhost:3000/api/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccount": "INVALID",
  "toAccount": "ALSO-INVALID",
  "amount": -50,
  "currency": "NOTREAL",
  "type": "invalid-type"
}
